        span.card__value= route.location
    p.card__data 
        | Difficulty: 
        span.card__value= route.difficulty 
    p.card__data 
        | Distance: 
        span.card__value= route.distance
        | Kms
    p.card__data
        | Elevation Gain: 
        span.card__value= route.elevationGain
        | m
    p.card__data 
        | Duration: 
        span.card__value= route.durationMins
        | min
